{"tid":998183,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"身為一個m男，終於搵到個s女","createTime":"2019-01-27T18:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T05:14:16.000Z","uid":64601,"like":194,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"64edfa9b68b5a3e094209df3479c7064182ffa5e","tid":998183,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的，平時自己衣著都好斯文，但暗地裡其實都幾敗類。<br />\n<br />\n咁有日行去日本名牌uniqlo，咁平時衣著都算幾型棍，都唔少女女向我投以挑逗嘅眼光。咁咁啱睇啱件衫，咪睇下，呢個時候有個mk妹行埋嚟，第一時間問我：你要s定要m㗎？哇！淫賤，我鍾意。我話:m嘅，仲要重m。呢一刻佢投以奇怪嘅目光望住我。我再問佢：你呢？佢答我s。<br />\n<br />\n咁大個仔第一次識到個s底女女，啱先仲抄咗個mk妹牌，有冇人答到我第一句開場白應該點講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9fe3f2ebc7a4f751a9587967219014a73a4ecc","tid":998183,"uid":3722,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:27:32.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"4f0dde34061ba083d73894766deb1d546ab33571","tid":998183,"uid":18485,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"今晚扑野夜唔夜耳"},{"pid":"5088ad516046b79d5cd08a8b8633f3314ae9d72c","tid":998183,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f0dde34061ba083d73894766deb1d546ab33571","tid":998183,"uid":18485,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"今晚扑野夜唔夜耳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:28:35.000Z","msg":"唔係要網調先㗎咩？"},{"pid":"6297d088ebdf4f13f039a68b8790b7d463434ec5","tid":998183,"uid":64601,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"5088ad516046b79d5cd08a8b8633f3314ae9d72c","tid":998183,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f0dde34061ba083d73894766deb1d546ab33571","tid":998183,"uid":18485,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:28:07.000Z","msg":"今晚扑野夜唔夜耳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:28:35.000Z","msg":"唔係要網調先㗎咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T18:29:07.000Z","msg":"已經set咗佢個名做主人<img src=\"/assets